metadata.name: w3bville
metadata.description:
This is the sad and funny tale of
the township of w3bville

Up here where the road
came to its definitive end

near the entrance to the old
abandoned silver mine

The residents of w3bville
were good

honest folks and
they liked their township

And while a and sentimental soul
grace was not for sale

though no elm tree had ever
cast its shadow in w3bville

they saw no reason
to change anything

That afternoon
the radio was playing softly
